{"type":"message","id":"c3acb325","parentId":"7b563c8a","timestamp":"2026-02-19T19:29:26.887Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Developing the Dashboard**\n\nI've successfully installed `textual` and am now building the directory structure. The plan is to have a dashboard component that pulls from `logs/openclaw.log`, or a dummy generator if needed. Currently, it'll display a \"Waiting for logs...\" message, awaiting log data to populate the display.\n\n\n**Implementing the Dashboard Code**\n\nI'm making progress on the `dashboard.py` file. I'm focusing on the `compose` method, adding a `Header`, `Footer`, and a `Log` widget for displaying log data. I'm also implementing a simulated log read, and will add actual log-reading functionality from `logs/openclaw.log` later. I've set up an interval to refresh the logs regularly, and I'm adding basic styles.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec_1771529366882_136","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir src/tui"},"thoughtSignature":""}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":12243,"output":667,"cacheRead":8917,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12910,"cost":{"input":0.024485999999999997,"output":0.008004,"cacheRead":0.0017834,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.034273399999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771529356099}}
{"type":"message","id":"4edf7438","parentId":"c3acb325","timestamp":"2026-02-19T19:29:27.095Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec_1771529366882_136","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Каталог: C:\\Users\\west2\\.openclaw\\workspace\\src\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\nd-----        19.02.2026     21:29                tui"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":207,"aggregated":"Каталог: C:\\Users\\west2\\.openclaw\\workspace\\src\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\nd-----        19.02.2026     21:29                tui","cwd":"C:\\Users\\west2\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1771529367094}}
{"type":"message","id":"ff6c4847","parentId":"4edf7438","timestamp":"2026-02-19T19:29:35.811Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Building the Dashboard**\n\nI'm currently focused on the creation of `src/tui/dashboard.py`. My primary objective is to implement the core dashboard functionality within this file, aiming for a robust and user-friendly design.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write_1771529375806_137","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"from textual.app import App, ComposeResult\nfrom textual.widgets import Header, Footer, Log, Static\nfrom textual.containers import Vertical\nimport os\nimport time\n\nclass DashboardApp(App):\n    \"\"\"A TUI Dashboard for OpenClaw.\"\"\"\n    \n    CSS = \"\"\"\n    #status {\n        background: $primary;\n        color: white;\n        text-align: center;\n        padding: 1;\n        height: 3;\n    }\n\n    Log {\n        height: 100%;\n        border: solid green;\n    }\n    \"\"\"\n\n    BINDINGS = [(\"q\", \"quit\", \"Quit\"), (\"r\", \"reload\", \"Reload\")]\n\n    def compose(self) -> ComposeResult:\n        yield Header()\n        with Vertical():\n            yield Static(\"OpenClaw Operational Dashboard - STATUS: ACTIVE\\n[Benjamin Protocol: Engaged]\", id=\"status\")\n            yield Log(id=\"log_view\", highlight=True, markup=True)\n        yield Footer()\n\n    def on_mount(self) -> None:\n        self.log_view = self.query_one(Log)\n        # Check logs every second\n        self.set_interval(1, self.update_logs)\n        self.last_pos = 0\n        self.log_file = \"logs/openclaw.log\" # Assuming this path relative to workspace root\n\n    def update_logs(self) -> None:\n        if os.path.exists(self.log_file):\n            try:\n                with open(self.log_file, \"r\") as f:\n                    f.seek(self.last_pos)\n                    lines = f.readlines()\n                    if lines:\n                        for line in lines:\n                             self.log_view.write(line.strip())\n                        self.last_pos = f.tell()\n            except Exception as e:\n                self.log_view.write(f\"[red]Error reading log: {e}[/]\")\n        else:\n             # Just a heartbeat if no log\n             self.log_view.write(f\"[{time.strftime('%H:%M:%S')}] [green]System operational.[/] Waiting for log file creation...\")\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    app = DashboardApp()\n    app.run()\n","file_path":"src/tui/dashboard.py"},"thoughtSignature":"CiQBjz1rX0aJmRiEcGJx+Rk4e4dHmTR/Sw6UT7flFlV8CXKn8RkKQAGPPWtfMR0DgZMJch9p8AthOE5HWjWykBdRf83Zcfu6zWr7L7Lu1QqCRKpoAmlkFGded/bK/S1cOT6MvIb/aUk="}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":12495,"output":549,"cacheRead":11613,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13044,"cost":{"input":0.02499,"output":0.006588,"cacheRead":0.0023226,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.033900599999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771529367096}}
