{"type":"message","id":"25fb8e4b","parentId":"c3747b21","timestamp":"2026-02-19T19:30:17.015Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating Progress So Far**\n\nI'm pleased to report that the personality injection is complete, all five agent config files are updated. Also, the TUI dashboard is up and running in `src/tui/dashboard.py`, thanks to `textual`. My attention has now shifted to the automated councils, and I'm currently focused on the `scripts/nightly_council.py` script.\n\n\n**Synthesizing The Output**\n\nI've successfully finalized all the necessary components. The agent config files are injected, and the dashboard is functional. I've also incorporated security measures into the nightly council script. Now, I'm focusing on crafting the final output, encompassing the thinking blocks, report sections, and final message, all to meet the user's specifications.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"message_1771529416997_140","name":"message","arguments":{"message":"<thinking>\n**Benjamin (Architect):** TUI dashboard deployed. `textual` library validated. Structure adheres to the Two-Step protocol: Blueprint -> Implementation. Status: OPTIMAL.\n**Lucas (Security):** `scripts/nightly_council.py` verified. Sanitization layer added for `API_KEY` and `SECRET`. Leakage vector neutralized. Approval granted.\n**Harper (Research):** Agent profiles updated. Emotional metadata indexed. This adds significant depth to the \"personality\" variable in our interactions. Fascinating.\n**Boss:** Excellent. The infrastructure is hardening. The Council is ready to convene.\n</thinking>\n\n# 🌙 Operation: Personality Injection & Roadmap Finale - COMPLETE\n\n## 1. Personality Injection (Configs)\n**Status:** ✅ **DONE**\nThe following agent profiles have been upgraded with **Emotional Profiles** and **MoE (Nightly Council) Obligations**:\n- `configs/agents/benjamin.md` (The Two-Step Coder)\n- `configs/agents/benjamin_tech.md` (The Architect)\n- `configs/agents/harper_search.md` (The Librarian)\n- `configs/agents/lucas.md` (The Paranoid Security Expert)\n- `configs/agents/lucas_qa.md` (The Gatekeeper)\n\n*New Capability:* Agents will now exhibit consistent emotional responses to stress/joy and are contractually obligated to report to the Nightly Council.\n\n## 2. TUI Dashboard (Benjamin)\n**Status:** ✅ **DONE**\n- **Location:** `src/tui/dashboard.py`\n- **Tech Stack:** Python + `textual` (installed and verified).\n- **Features:**\n    - **Header:** System Status (Active).\n    - **Body:** Live Log Tail (monitors `logs/openclaw.log`).\n    - **Footer:** Command hints.\n- **Usage:** Run `python src/tui/dashboard.py` in a separate terminal to monitor operations.\n\n## 3. Automated Councils (Boss/Lucas)\n**Status:** ✅ **DONE**\n- **Refined Script:** `scripts/nightly_council.py`\n- **Security Upgrade:** Added `sanitize_content()` function.\n    - **Action:** Scans all output lines for `API_KEY`, `SECRET`, `TOKEN`, `PASSWORD`.\n    - **Result:** Replaces sensitive lines with `[REDACTED: SENSITIVE DATA DETECTED]` before writing to the daily report.\n\n## Final Message\nThe stage is set. The actors know their lines (and their feelings). The theater (TUI) is open. The critics (Council) are watching.\n\n**Ready for the next act.**","action":"send"},"thoughtSignature":""}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":15264,"output":730,"cacheRead":11717,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15994,"cost":{"input":0.030528,"output":0.00876,"cacheRead":0.0023434000000000003,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.041631400000000006}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771529405939}}
